{"title": "Stimulation of human-growth-hormone secretion by L-dopa", "url": "https://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJM197012242832602", "author": "AE Boyd III and HE Lebovitz and JB Pfeiffer", "abstract": "The effect of L-dopa, a precursor of Central-nervous-system catecholamines, on growth-hormone secretion was studied in a group of patients with Parkinson's disease undergoing treatment with the drug. Oral doses (0.5 g) caused a significant rise in plasma growth \u2026"}